  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe value work-life balance and expect you to manage your time effectively to meet business needs. Your working hours and schedule will be established by your manager and may vary depending on your role and departmental requirements. This policy outlines our standard workweek, expectations for attendance, and general guidelines regarding flexible work arrangements, meal periods, and rest breaks. We encourage open communication with your manager regarding any scheduling needs or concerns.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
